                <section id="other" data-w-id="01cf29dd-aca9-bfe2-0b66-2b79eff87f9d" class="section-home-other">
                    <!-- faq section -->
                    <div id="faq" class="faq">
                        <div class="container-large">
                            <section class="faq-heading">
                                <div style="-webkit-transform:translate3d(0, 100%, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-moz-transform:translate3d(0, 100%, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);-ms-transform:translate3d(0, 100%, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);transform:translate3d(0, 100%, 0) scale3d(1, 1, 1) rotateX(0) rotateY(0) rotateZ(0) skew(0, 0);color:rgba(0,0,0,0)" class="text_eyebrow">Details</div>
                                <h2 class="text-color-black">Frequently Asked Questions(f.a.qs)</h2>
                            </section>
                            <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordionFlushExample">
                                <!-- FAQ Item 1 -->
                                <div class="accordion-item">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingOne">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseOne">
                                           <b>Q:How does Xofle's remote hiring platform work?</b> 
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="flush-collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                        Xofle simplifies remote hiring for you <br>
                                        <b>Step 1: Understanding Your Needs</b>
                                        <p>We start by comprehensively understanding your hiring needs. Whether you're looking for fresh talent, seasoned professionals, or specific skill sets, we tailor our approach to meet your unique requirements.</p>
                                        <br>
                                        <b>Step 2: Shortlisting from a Diverse Pool</b>
                                        <p>Based on your criteria, we curate a list of shortlisted applicants from our diverse talent pool. Each candidate is carefully selected to match your specific job prerequisites.</p>
                                        <br>
                                        <b>Step 3: Organizing Online Tests and Interviews</b>
                                        <p>To further refine your selection, we assist in organizing online tests and interviews.</p>
                                        <br>
                                        <b>Step 4: Onboarding and Beyond</b>
                                        <p>Once you've selected the ideal candidate, our support extends beyond the hiring process. We assist in onboarding and provide ongoing support for any post-selection requirements. Whether it's providing laptops, conducting background checks, or offering legal assistance, we're your trusted partner in India.</p>
                                        <br>
                                        <b>Streamlined Process, Optimal Talent</b>
                                        <p>Xofle streamlines the entire hiring process, ensuring that you obtain the best talent with minimal effort. Our commitment is to make remote hiring a hassle-free and rewarding experience for your team.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- FAQ Item 2 -->
                                <div class="accordion-item">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingTwo">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseTwo">
                                            <b>Q: How can a company reduce costs by remote hiring?</b>
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="flush-collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            In the evolving landscape of work, remote hiring has become a strategic choice for companies aiming to optimize costs and access a diverse talent pool. Here's how the math works:
                                            <br>
                                            <b>1.Global Talent Access:</b>
                                            <p> With the proliferation of remote work conditions, hiring from a global talent pool becomes feasible, especially for tech-related roles. Remote work is increasingly preferred, offering improved work-life balance.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>2.Cost Parity Advantage:</b>
                                            <p> Consider this scenario – hiring a skilled engineer in a first-world country might cost <b>$100,000</b> , while a similarly qualified engineer in a third-world country like India,pakistan say India might command <b>$20,000</b>. This substantial difference, often due to cost parity adjustments, translates to significant savings for your company.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>3.Quality Without Compromise:</b>
                                            <p> Remote hiring allows you to access top-tier talent in India without compromising on quality. Engineers from remote locations are as qualified and possess strong communicative skills.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>The Xofle Advantage:</b>
                                            <p>While the cost savings are evident, navigating remote hiring requires support. This is where Xofle steps in:</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>-Access to Quality Candidates:</b>
                                            <p>Xofle provides access to a pool of skilled candidates, streamlining your hiring process.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>End-to-End Support:</b>
                                            <p> Beyond candidate selection, we assist in various aspects, including testing, interviews, and comprehensive onboarding support.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>Cost-Effective Onboarding Services:</b>
                                            <p> From background checks to legal and administrative assistance, Xofle serves as your trusted partner. Importantly, you only pay for our services after you've extended an offer letter.</p>
            
                                            <i>Embrace the cost-efficient approach of remote hiring with Xofle, where quality meets savings seamlessly.</i>
            
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                
                                <!-- FAQ Item 3 -->
                                <div class="accordion-item">
                                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="flush-headingThree">
                                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#flush-collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="flush-collapseThree">
                                        <b>Q:Give me a detailed view of the services included</b>
                                        </button>
                                    </h2>
                                    <div id="flush-collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="flush-headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionFlushExample">
                                        <div class="accordion-body">
                                            At Xofle, our services are designed to be adaptable and cater to the unique requirements of your company's hiring journey. Here's a breakdown:
                                            <br>
                                            <b>a. Diverse Talent Pool Access:</b>
                                            <p>Our platform grants you access to a diverse pool of candidates, ranging from freshers to experienced professionals.Customization is key – we assist you based on your specific hiring needs.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>b. Indian Job Insights:</b>
                                            <p>Receive insights into competitive salaries for various roles, ensuring that your compensation packages remain attractive.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>c. Customized Testing and Interviews:</b>
                                            <p>Tailor your hiring process by choosing testing and interviewing methods that align with your company's preferences.We handle the logistics, from communicating details to candidates to scheduling and facilitating interviews efficiently.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>d. Onboarding Support:</b>
                                            <p>For startups or enterprises, we provide comprehensive onboarding assistance. If you're a startup, it may involve setting up software, while for enterprises, it could extend to legal and administrative support.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>e. Legal and Compliance Guidance:</b>
                                            <p>Ensure a smooth legal journey with our guidance, whether it's background checks, provident fund(indian 401K) compliance, or other legal aspects.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>f. IT and Administrative Help:</b>
                                            <p>From IT support to administrative tasks, Xofle serves as your end-to-end partner.
                                                Assistance during onboarding and deboarding ensures a seamless experience for both employers and employees.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <b>g. Cost Savings Up to 80%:</b>
                                            <p>Recognizing the value of remote work, Xofle facilitates the process to help employees find remote jobs, promoting a healthier work-life balance. <br> For companies, this translates to significant cost savings, up to 80%.</p>
                                            <br>
                                            <br>
                                            <p>Embrace the efficiency of remote hiring with Xofle, where every service is crafted to enhance your hiring experience, making it streamlined, cost-effective, and tailored to your unique needs.</p>
            
            
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
